title: Alison Brie / Head Trauma & Vision Loss
description: Priyanka and Sean predict the next big medical advancements. A caller is blindsided by his Toxoplasmosis diagnosis. Alison Brie shares her rare and interesting story of the time she lost her vision after hitting her head. Sean and Alison discuss wearing many hats in Hollywood.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
